('gen17Srv7Nme3_99960_1335625786', '1', 'Tax Evasion', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', ''Segoe UI'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(232, 232, 232); ">\r\n	Tax evasion and tax dodging are very pure but once you are quote your business is in financial distress.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', ''Segoe UI'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(232, 232, 232); ">\r\n	1. Documents of taxation<br />\r\n	2. The link between taxation ,accounting and business success<br />\r\n	3. The role of government in taxation matters<br />\r\n	4. The role of private sector in taxation matters<br />\r\n	5. The different legislative framework of taxation<br />\r\n	6. The business taxation systems(types and models)</p>', 'evasion, tax, accounting', '2012-04-28 17:09:46', NULL, 'false', 12),
